title: Lets Talk Quarterbacks
description:
Wendi Nix, Tom Luginbill, and E.J. Manuel discuss the Big Ten's decision to do away with their minimum game rule. Wright Thompson joins the show to discuss the manning family, and Tom and E.J. rank their top 5 quarterbacks.
